high_descs: Turn left, step forward, turn right, move forward, then turn left to face the counter adjacent to the stove.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter, next to the tomato.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Look up on the counter.
Put the butter knife on the counter, to the right of the tomato.
Look down on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the counter.
Turn left, go straight, then turn right to face the sink.
Wash the tomato slice in the sink.
Turn around, move forward, then turn right to face the trash bin.
Put the tomato slice in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of tomato in the trash.

high_descs: Go face the kitchen counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Use the knife to cut the pepper on the counter.
Look at the counter with the knife to find a spot.
Put the knife back down on the counter.
Look down at the pepper.
Pick up a slice of the pepper from the counter.
Bring the pepper with you and go to the kitchen sink.
Put the pepper in the sink and wash it, then pick it up again.
Bring the pepper with you over to the trash can.
Put the pepper slice in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Throw a clean piece of pepper away.

high_descs: Turn right and face the counter with the toaster on it
Grab the knife off of the counter
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices
Look up at the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Look down at the counter
Grab a slice of tomato off of the counter
Turn left and go to the sink
Wash the tomato in the sink and then take it out
Turn around and go to the trash can
Put the tomato in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Moving a tomato slice to the trash can
